EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

The 30th day of September 2020 is appointed as the day on which Sections 62, 
63, 64, 65 and 66 of the Children’s Health Act 2018 (No. 27 of 2018) shall come 
into operation.
